# Local-only git worktrees. Convention is to keep them under .worktrees/
# inside the main checkout (the path the host signing server accepts);
# anything under there is by definition a working copy, never authored
# content. Without this entry, `git worktree add .worktrees/<name>` leaves
# .worktrees/ as an untracked directory in the parent checkout and the
# stop hook fires.
.worktrees/